# Input

```scss
.urls {
	string-plus-variable: url( "../test/" + $test-path );
	string-plus-string: url( "../test/" + "static/test.jpg" );
	string-plus-number: url( 'v'+1 );
	string-plus-dimension: url( 'v'+1px );
	interpolated-string-plus: url( "#{$bg}" + ".png" );
	commented-plus: url( $test-path /* c */ + "static/test.jpg" );
	raw-interpolation: url( fudge#{$x}.css );
	import-url: url( //fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=#{get-font-family("Roboto")}:100 );
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.urls {
	string-plus-variable: url("../test/" + $test-path);
	string-plus-string: url("../test/" + "static/test.jpg");
	string-plus-number: url("v" + 1);
	string-plus-dimension: url("v" + 1px);
	interpolated-string-plus: url("#{$bg}" + ".png");
	commented-plus: url($test-path /* c */ + "static/test.jpg");
	raw-interpolation: url(fudge#{$x}.css);
	import-url: url(//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=#{get-font-family("Roboto")}:100);
}

```

# Lines exceeding max width of 80 characters
```
    9: 	import-url: url(//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=#{get-font-family("Roboto")}:100);
```
